# MODULAR SCHOOLING SYSTEM - IMPLEMENTATION CHECKLIST

## üìã PHASE 1: FOUNDATION (Weeks 1-2)

### Database Schema Extensions
- [x] Create `modules` table with all metadata fields
  - [x] Add id, title, description, category, difficulty
  - [x] Add estimated_duration, prerequisites (JSON), learning_objectives (JSON)
  - [x] Add theme_override (JSON), author, version
  - [x] Add timestamps, is_published, order_index
- [x] Create `submodules` table
  - [x] Add id, module_id, title, template_type
  - [x] Add content (JSON), styling (JSON), duration_estimate
  - [x] Add notes (admin-only), order_index, timestamps
  - [x] Set up foreign key cascade on module deletion
- [x] Create `media_assets` table
  - [x] Add id, filename, original_name, mime_type, size
  - [x] Add storage_type, storage_path, thumbnail_path
  - [x] Add tags (JSON), uploaded_by, created_at
- [x] Create `quiz_questions` table
  - [x] Add id, submodule_id, question_text, question_type
  - [x] Add options (JSON), correct_answer (JSON), points
  - [x] Add explanation, order_index
- [x] Create `quiz_responses` table
  - [x] Add id, session_id, user_id, question_id
  - [x] Add answer (JSON), is_correct, time_taken, created_at
- [x] Create `poll_results` table
  - [x] Add id, submodule_id, session_id, user_id
  - [x] Add option_selected, created_at
- [x] Create `wordcloud_entries` table
  - [x] Add id, submodule_id, session_id, user_id
  - [x] Add word, created_at
- [x] Create `user_progress` table
  - [x] Add id, user_id, module_id, submodule_id
  - [x] Add status, score, time_spent
  - [x] Add last_accessed, completed_at
- [x] Create `user_notes` table
  - [x] Add id, user_id, submodule_id, note_text
  - [x] Add created_at, updated_at
- [x] Create `user_bookmarks` table
  - [x] Add id, user_id, submodule_id, created_at
- [x] Create `sessions` table
  - [x] Add id, module_id, current_submodule_id
  - [x] Add started_at, ended_at, participants_count
- [x] Create `app_gallery_items` table
  - [x] Add id, submodule_id, app_name, description
  - [x] Add screenshot_url, prompt_used, app_url
  - [x] Add order_index, created_at
- [x] Create `app_feedback` table
  - [x] Add id, app_id, session_id, user_id
  - [x] Add feedback_type (up/down/neutral), created_at
- [x] Run database migration script
- [ ] Test all table relationships and constraints

### Backend API Routes
- [x] Create `/api/module-creator/modules` endpoints
  - [x] GET /api/module-creator/modules - List all modules
  - [x] GET /api/module-creator/modules/:id - Get single module
  - [x] POST /api/module-creator/modules - Create new module
  - [x] PUT /api/module-creator/modules/:id - Update module
  - [x] DELETE /api/module-creator/modules/:id - Delete module
- [x] Create `/api/module-creator/submodules` endpoints
  - [x] GET /api/module-creator/modules/:moduleId/submodules - List submodules
  - [x] GET /api/module-creator/submodules/:id - Get single submodule
  - [x] POST /api/module-creator/modules/:moduleId/submodules - Create submodule
  - [x] PUT /api/module-creator/submodules/:id - Update submodule
  - [x] DELETE /api/module-creator/submodules/:id - Delete submodule
  - [x] PUT /api/module-creator/submodules/reorder - Reorder submodules
- [x] Create `/api/module-creator/media` endpoints
  - [x] GET /api/module-creator/media - List media assets
  - [x] POST /api/module-creator/media/upload - Upload media file
  - [x] DELETE /api/module-creator/media/:id - Delete media asset
  - [ ] GET /api/module-creator/media/:id/thumbnail - Get thumbnail
- [ ] Add authentication middleware for admin routes
- [x] Add file upload middleware (Multer)
- [x] Add error handling middleware

